@{
    ViewBag.Title = "Home Page";
}

<body>
    <div class="jumbotron">
        <h1 style="color:darkgreen">Welcome to Recycle Guide!</h1>
        <h2>Recycle in Australia</h2>
        <img src="~/Resources/HomePage-Image.jpeg" width="1000" height="600" alt="HeadingImage">
        <p class="lead">
            Between 2017 and 2018, 9.4% of the plastic wastes were recovered in Australia.
            According to a report published by European Environmental Bureau (EEB), Australia has has a total recycling rate of 41%,
            ranked as 21st in the entire world. The country with the highest recycling rate, Germany, successfully recycled 66.1% of their total wastes,
            which is more than 1.5 times than that of Australia.
        </p>
        <p><a href="https://www.awe.gov.au/environment/protection/waste" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg">Learn More &raquo;</a></p>
    </div>

    <div class="row-1">
        <h2>Waste Bin Type in Australia</h2>
        <p style="font-size:larger">
            Waste bins are essential in keeping the trash around Australia well-managed.
            It is an essential tool in waste management methods.
        </p>
        <h3>What Do We Have</h3>
        <div class="col-md-4">
            <img src="~/Resources/general.png" width="250" height="300" alt="HeadingImage">
            <h4>General Waste Bin</h4>
            <p>
                Color: Red
            </p>
            <p>
                Toward: Landfill
            </p>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-4">
            <img src="~/Resources/recycle.png" width="250" height="300" alt="HeadingImage">
            <h4>Mixed Recyclables Bin</h4>
            <p>
                Color: Yellow
            </p>
            <p>
                Toward: Recovery Facility
            </p>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-4">
            <img src="~/Resources/organic.png" width="250" height="300" alt="HeadingImage">
            <h4>Organic Waste Bin</h4>
            <p>
                Color: Green
            </p>
            <p>
                Toward: Farming Indusry
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="row-2">
        <h3>Recycle Process</h3>
        <p>Recycling, recovery and reprocessing of waste materials for use in new products.</p>
        <h6>@Html.ActionLink("How Does The Process Work?", "About", "Home")</h6>
            <div class="row-3">
                <h3 align="right" , style="color:gray">About Us</h3>
                <h5 align="right">@Html.ActionLink("Get Team Info", "Contact", "Home")</h5>
            </div>
    </div>

    <style>
           body {
                    background: url('../../Resources/BlueSky.jpeg') no-repeat;
                    background-size: 100% 100%;
                }
           img {
                    display: block;
               }
    </style>

 </body >
